    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i see what you mean about the tension between sovereignty and intervention. but some critics argue that the UN is actually just a tool used by powerful nations to enforce their own interests under the guise of \"global peace.\" do you think the UN's structure is actually designed to enable this kind of hegemony, or is that just a conspiracy theory view?",
